title: Sex For Survival
description:
As an occult club, all of us did rituals on a 1,000-year-old sacred tree in the back of the school to prove occult.

Then, the sacred tree really talked to us...!

"Don't curse so that your wishes will come true."

"If you want to survive... have sex!"
author: Sihyun
